OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FJersey's government has decided to pay
OL,7,Foff all outstanding debt from the 2024
OL,8,FBattle of Flowers' event, despite
OL,9,Fpreviously telling ITV News that
OL,10,Forganisers should cover their own
OL,11,Fcosts.
OL,13,FLast year, Battle made a loss of more
OL,14,Fthan #350,000, with many exhibitors
OL,15,Fand creditors not being paid as a
OL,16,Fresult - despite a record #270,000
OL,17,Fgovernment grant.
