OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FDeputy Kirsten Morel, the island's
OL,7,FMinister for Sustainable Economic
OL,8,FDevelopment, told ITV News in March
OL,9,Fthat the "Government isn't there to
OL,10,Fbail out and just pay off the debt".
OL,12,FHe added: "The Battle of Flowers
OL,13,FAssociation have sufficient assets for
OL,14,Fus to work out a way for them to pay
OL,15,Foff their own debts."
