OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FHowever, the Government has now
OL,7,Fconfirmed a bailout costing #121,000,
OL,8,Fonly a few months after announcing up
OL,9,Fto #220,000 of grants to fund this
OL,10,Fyear's smaller celebrations: ITV News
OL,11,Funderstands this latter figure now
OL,12,Fstands at #158,000.
OL,14,FThe payment to cover debts has been
OL,15,Fmade as an advance on future funding
OL,16,Ffor the Battle of Flowers, raising
OL,17,Fquestions about whether the event will
OL,18,Fever return to its former scale.
