OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FSteve Bouchard from The Optimists
OL,7,FClub, which won last year's event,
OL,8,Fsays: "It is a concern because it's
OL,9,Fleaving a legacy behind, people will
OL,10,Fhave to take on a debt they didn't
OL,11,Fincur.
OL,13,F"But that's the way it is and at least
OL,14,Fwe have a Battle on this year."
