OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FIn a statement, the island's
OL,7,Fgovernment explains: "The Battle of
OL,8,FFlowers is an essential fixture in
OL,9,FJersey's summer calendar, bringing our
OL,10,Fcommunity together through thousands
OL,11,Fof hours of volunteering and drawing
OL,12,Fcrowds to the centre of town.
OL,14,F"Ministers have provided this payment
OL,15,Fto enable the parade to proceed this
OL,16,Fyear."
