OL,3,CGovernment u-turn sees taxpayer cover
OL,4,C#121,000 for event overspend
OL,6,FBen Shelton from Age Concern explains:
OL,7,F"I'm the chair of two charities that
OL,8,Fdo really good work in the island and
OL,9,Fwe could do much better with that
OL,10,Fmoney than wasting and squandering it
OL,11,Fon grants that aren't properly
OL,12,Finvestigated and aren't given out in
OL,13,Fthe right manner."
OL,15,FA scaled-back Battle will be held
OL,16,Flater this week under a new leadership
OL,17,Fcommittee, with smaller floats and two
OL,18,Ffree parades through the town.
